User Data Deletion Instructions

Simple Event Finder allows users to request deletion of any personal data associated with their use of the app.

To request deletion of your data, email:

philipthegingermclaughlin@gmail.com

Use the subject line:

Data Deletion Request - Simple Event Finder

Please include the Facebook name or account ID associated with the app login, if available.

After receiving the request, we will delete any stored user profile information and saved user-specific event data associated with that account, unless we are required to retain certain information for legal or security reasons.

You may also remove the app from your Facebook account by going to:

Facebook Settings → Apps and Websites → Simple Event Finder → Remove

Once your request is processed, we will confirm deletion by email.
